      "act": "THE IMPLICATION",
      "t_start": 106,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10,
      "narration_text": "Turn the scattering length to infinity and the gas forms a Bose-Einstein condensate with the strongest possible interactions. Set it to zero and the gas becomes nearly ideal.",
